  <h2>Faith Is the Starting Point</h2>
  <p class="lead">Everything on this site flows from one core belief: you were made on purpose, for a purpose. Not a vague motivational idea &mdash; a real, grounded conviction that God has a plan for your life that is bigger than your current circumstances, your past mistakes, or your present doubts.</p>
  <p>The <strong>#FaithFocusFinish</strong> framework starts with Faith because everything else builds on it. When you're rooted in that, focus becomes clearer and finishing becomes possible. Without it, you're just grinding with no anchor.</p>
  <p>This section isn't about being preachy. It's about being honest. About the real work it takes to trust God's timing when things aren't moving. About choosing faith over fear when both options are on the table. About what it looks like to bring your faith into the everyday &mdash; your goals, your habits, your setbacks.</p>
